'''Clinton Young''', best known as '''Clint Young''', was a senior artist for LucasArts and Lucasfilm, and worked as the lead for several projects.
{{Mediacat|imagecat=images by Clint Young}}
He has also been credited as a writer on several LucasArts titles including [[Star Wars: Episode I Racer|''Star Wars'': Episode I ''Racer'']] (where the character [[Cy Yunga]] was named after him) and ''[[Star Wars: Bounty Hunter]]''. Clint Young was also credited with creating 3D models in [[Star Wars: Jedi Knight: Dark Forces II]]. Young was also a voice actor for [[B1-Series battle droid]]s and [[B2 super battle droid/Legends|super battle droids]] in ''[[Star Wars: Republic Commando]] in addition to several other characters in the Lucasfilm / LucasArts umbrella.'' He has several conceptual sites including blog sites where his art work is displayed, most recent as a senior lead concept artist on the video game ''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''.

